      "HAWAIIAL\nHAWAIIAN AIRLINES\nDC-9 Royal Fan Jets make each island less\nthan 30 minutes away from Honolulu.\nHawaiian has served the entire state for\nover 37 years and is Holder of the World's\nSafety Record.\nAloha!\nWe at Hawaiian Airlines wish\nyou luck in the AAL, PAA \u0026\nHAL Contest and it will be\npleasure having you aboard\nHawaiian.\nGood Luck and see you soon.\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE\nMISS DIANA BLATTER\nDave Keeton\nRegional Sales Manager\n2015\n0745"
